{"tid":2139101,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英潮玩「磁釣」隨時吸起舊武器","createTime":"2020-08-04T05:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T09:37:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9f0bb7bd5dff2280520005965cca3acdd7610189","tid":2139101,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T05:20:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200804/NP73GOBZJIGLWARXJUCT3UXAAA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200804%2FNP73GOBZJIGLWARXJUCT3UXAAA%2F&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd2yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=bcf12e27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200804%2FNP73GOBZJIGLWARXJUCT3UXAAA%2F&h=c2fee301\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200804/NP73GOBZJIGLWARXJUCT3UXAAA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n英潮玩「磁釣」隨時吸起舊武器<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8hKFvvJwWh_rEEAOxv13eOBrWrc=/591x327/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YHBEIIWXLIQSHS5LBAA7P4RMAI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8hKFvvJwWh_rEEAOxv13eOBrWrc%3D%2F591x327%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYHBEIIWXLIQSHS5LBAA7P4RMAI.jpg&h=ef092999&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n磁釣者曾釣起18磅未爆炸彈。<br />\n<br />\n英國近年越來越多民眾熱衷於到運河或池塘邊玩「磁釣」。與一般釣魚不同，他們會用繩索繫上強力磁石，並拋到水中吸起被遺棄的物件，釣來的包括廢鐵、餐具、槍枝，甚至連停車場售票機都有。<br />\n<br />\n視作親子活動<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。但他最愛的收穫還是一個1970至80年代停車場售票機。<br />\n<br />\n英國像拉姆福特般愛好磁釣的人越來越多，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。他們就曾釣到的舊物包括反坦克子彈和武士刀。<br />\n<br />\n雖然大多磁釣愛好者都覺得興趣有助清理河道，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n英國《泰晤士報》"},{"pid":"245fc3a8566ecc1ebf74efe25a593154f06e78e0","tid":2139101,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T05:21:42.000Z","msg":"淘寶<img src=\"/assets/fac