曾釣到的舊物包括反坦克子彈和武士刀。<br />\n<br />\n雖然大多磁釣愛好者都覺得興趣有助清理河道，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n英國《泰晤士報》"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T05:25:13.000Z","msg":"想要武士刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de8b692f9d6f123a402ac7a6a31010727d0c6dcb","tid":2139101,"uid":210612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T05:26:09.000Z","msg":"有嘢執順便清理河道 好過釣埋啲重金屬魚"},{"pid":"bdf819f2b2d8cb2845936596134a0d942f144acb","tid":2139101,"uid":55321,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T05:26:49.000Z","msg":"磁釣點可以冇<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/8/8e/Chilunzine.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20091201113923\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F8%2F8e%2FChilunzine.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20091201113923&h=d52a2054&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45d6f5d4e8edd431cf638b8c62c81503171ec264","tid":2139101,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T05:31:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88b0177e898618a71085c26bf2f51f46744414e2","tid":2139101,"uid":81824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"467e7a4dc18b71436fd51ea5dac2a9aaf3c7481c","tid":2139101,"uid":58209,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T05:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BS04Uhk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBS04Uhk.jpg&h=f8b400fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T05:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2016/20/68/qpmZnqOWkaKVqaQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2016%2F20%2F68%2FqpmZnqOWkaKVqaQ.jpg&h=afb31c1f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1de3a8488110a328a04d37729a0265ee49f86f74","tid":2139101,"uid":187493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T05:47:41.000Z","msg":"停車場售票機<img src=\"/assets/fa